| email_tokens | tokenHash | String(64) | unique | raw token never stored |

### 6.5 Data Migration & Seeding Strategy

- **Migrations:** Managed by **`migrate-mongo`** with versioned scripts checked into Git; `up`/`down` symmetry mandatory.
- **Seeds:** Two profiles — `dev` (50 users, 2 000 log entries across 30 days, 20 articles, 30 products) and `prod` (one bootstrap admin from env vars; empty content).
- **Pre-Deploy:** `npm run migrate` runs in CI; deploy aborts on migration failure.

### 6.6 Backup & Recovery Approach

| Aspect | Specification | Driving Requirement |
|---|---|---|
| **Backup Frequency** | Continuous oplog backup (Atlas Cloud Backup) + nightly snapshots | NFR-12 |
| **Retention** | 7 daily, 4 weekly, 12 monthly | Operational practice |
| **Storage** | Atlas-managed, geo-redundant | Disaster recovery |
| **RPO** | ≤ 5 minutes (oplog-based) | NFR-12 (better than 1h target) |
| **RTO** | ≤ 1 hour | NFR-12 |
| **Verification** | Quarterly restore-to-staging drill | Validates RTO |

